works.description:
Superior in every sense, the Bugatti  
Veyron has already earned itself a name in car history as an undisputed  
classic. We have earlier seen some of the most exotic and expensive
Bugatti  
Veyrons, and now, we have a yacht that draws inspiration from this
gorgeous  
Bugatti Veyron Grand Sport Sang Bleu supercar. Designed by Ben Walsh, the 

30-foot Sang Bleu yacht concept enjoys a sleek silhouette and a carbon  
fiber and aluminum exterior.
